{
  "stem": "16163.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He went to Auschwitz and didn't come back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were bothering us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were calling us names, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And even some of the parents of the children did that also.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was Germany in those times.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Many times, many times when we were kids.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got beaten up in the streets, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was a way of surviving and living then already.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were terrible upset, because they couldn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember that, at one time, I got into a fight with three boys on the street.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Three against me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was always taller and bigger than Gunter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when they started in with him, I [INAUDIBLE] at the time too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from one of the boys, the father was a friend, still, at that particular time, of my father.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he came to-- he took me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He must have seen the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was, like seven years, eight years old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He took me and brought me home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But his son was the one who beat me up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So this was like one of those things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, sometimes we got beaten up, bloodied, got blue marks, got away with it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were little.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I was a fighter, all the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He would have been a fighter if he was bigger.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was-- matter of fact, he was born in 1926.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he was a year older than me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was so tiny at the time when school started for him, which would have been a year before, that they didn't take him.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not because of that he was Jewish, that he physically was not fully developed as a six-year-old one should be.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that's how come he started school with me.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
